get zone object

Source: R/get_zone_object.R
get_zone_object.Rd

get zone object

Usage

get_zone_object(grid, zoo_grid)

Arguments

grid

grid object

zoo_grid

zoo grid object

Value

zone object

Examples

data(grid)
grid$zone[2] <- 2
data(skink_grid)
get_zone_object(grid, skink_grid)
#> # A tibble: 2 × 3
#>    zone   obs n_grids
#>   <dbl> <dbl>   <int>
#> 1     1  5811      15
#> 2     2   917       1
